  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Warehouse Executive",
  "description": "<p>Warehouse Executive and play a crucial role in ensuring the efficient packing of high-quality fruits and vegetables to meet customer requirements. Responsibilities:</p><p>1. <strong>Packing Fresh Produce:</strong>Efficiently pack fresh produce, including fruits and vegetables, according to specific requirements.</p><p>2. <strong>Night Shift Operations:</strong>Perform general work tasks during the night shift, contributing to a seamless workflow.</p><p>3. <strong>Customer Engagement:</strong>Listen to customer needs and assist them in finding the perfect products.<br />Build and constantly enhance product knowledge, delivering information in engaging ways.</p><p>4. <strong>Visual Merchandising:</strong>Set up attractive product displays and promotional booths to attract customer attention.</p><p>5. <strong>Presentations and Demonstrations:</strong>Deliver presentations and product demonstrations to customers and stakeholders.</p><p>6. <strong>Relationship Building:</strong>Engage in meaningful interactions, fostering good relationships with customers.</p><p>7. <strong>Sampling and Feedback:</strong>Distribute product samples and provide valuable feedback for continuous improvement.</p><p>8. <strong>Customer Follow-up:</strong>Follow up with customers, offering guidance on product selection and ensuring satisfaction.</p><p>9. <strong>Sales Targets:</strong>Meet daily sales targets and submit comprehensive sales reports.</p><p>10. <strong>Networking and Business Development:</strong>Network with relevant stakeholders and actively search for new business opportunities.</p><p><strong>Night Shift Commitment:</strong>Must be available to work during the night shift.</p><p>We appreciate your interest in joining our team. Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. All resumes received will be used for recruitment purposes only.</p><p>EA License ID: 18C9520</p><p>EA Registration ID: R1765753</p>",
